\end_inset

分别设定为
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha=-\lambda(v_{t}-\bar{v}),\beta=1$
\end_inset

，于是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dS_{t}=\mu_{t}S_{t}dt+\sqrt{v_{t}}S_{t}dZ_{t1}\tag{2.1}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dv_{t}=-\lambda(v_{t}-\bar{v})dt+\eta\sqrt{v_{t}}dZ_{t2}\tag{2.2}
\]

\end_inset

其中，
\begin_inset Formula $E(dZ_{t1}dZ_{t2})=\rho dt$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

表示
\begin_inset Formula $v_{t}$
\end_inset

回复到其长期均值
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{v}$
\end_inset

的速度。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
上面将瞬时方差设定为一种平方根过程(square root process或CIR process——Cox,Ingersoll, and Ross(1985)
)。将
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha,\beta$
\end_inset

代入(1.3)可得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial V}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}vS^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial S^{2}}+\rho\eta vS\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial v\partial S}+\frac{1}{2}\eta^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial v^{2}}+rS\frac{\partial V}{\partial S}-rV=\lambda(v-\bar{v})\frac{\partial V}{\partial v}\tag{2.3}
\]

\end_inset

其中，我们假定：the Heston process generates the risk-neutral measure so the market
 price of volatility risk 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

in the general valuation equation(1.3) is set to 0 in equation (2.3)。
