\begin_layout Subsection
Heston dynamics
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
首先，the Heston dynamics为
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
dS_{t}/S_{t} & =rdt+\sqrt{v_{t}}dZ_{t1}\\
dv_{t} & =\kappa(\bar{v}-v_{t})dt+\sigma\sqrt{v_{t}}dZ_{t2}\\
E[dZ_{t1}dZ_{t2}] & =\rho dt\tag{A.1}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
the Heston PDE
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Form a portfolio consisting of one option 
\begin_inset Formula $V=V(S,v,t)$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta$
\end_inset

units of the stock 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, and 
\begin_inset Formula $\phi$
\end_inset

units of another option 
\begin_inset Formula $U=U(S,v,t)$
\end_inset

 that is used to hedge the volatility。then the portfolio value：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Pi=V+\Delta S+\phi U
\]

\end_inset

假定组合是self-financing，于是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
d\Pi=dV+\Delta dS+\phi dU
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Portfolio dynamics。对
\begin_inset Formula $dV$
\end_inset

应用Ito's lemma，于是：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
dV=\frac{\partial V}{\partial t}dt+\frac{\partial V}{\partial S}dS+\frac{\partial V}{\partial v}dv+\frac{1}{2}vS^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial S^{2}}dt+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial v^{2}}dt+\sigma v\rho S\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial v\partial S}dt
\]

\end_inset

同样对
\begin_inset Formula $dU$
\end_inset

应用Ito's lemma会有相思的结果。因此
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
d\Pi & =dV+\Delta dS+\phi dU\\
 & =\{\frac{\partial V}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}vS^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial S^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho S\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial v\partial S}\}dt+\\
 & \phi\{\frac{\partial U}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}vS^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial S^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho S\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v\partial S}\}dt+\\
 & \{\frac{\partial V}{\partial S}+\phi\frac{\partial U}{\partial S}+\Delta\}dS+\{\frac{\partial V}{\partial v}+\phi\frac{\partial U}{\partial v}\}dv\tag{A.2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
the riskless portfolio。令式(A.2)中的
\begin_inset Formula $dS$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $dv$
\end_inset

项为0，则
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\phi=-\frac{\frac{\partial V}{\partial v}}{\frac{\partial U}{\partial v}}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta=-\phi\frac{\partial U}{\partial S}-\frac{\partial V}{\partial S}\tag{A.3}
\]

\end_inset

此时，组合是一个无风险资产，于是收益率为无风险收益，即
\begin_inset Formula $d\Pi=r\Pi dt$
\end_inset

，因此
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
d\Pi & =\{\frac{\partial V}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}vS^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial S^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho S\frac{\partial^{2}V}{\partial v\partial S}\}dt+\\
 & \phi\{\frac{\partial U}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}vS^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial S^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho S\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v\partial S}\}dt\\
 & \equiv(A+\phi B)dt\\
 & =r\Pi dt
\end{align*}

\end_inset

即
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A+\phi B=r(V+\Delta S+\phi U)
\]

\end_inset

将(A.3)式代入可得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{A-rV+rS\frac{\partial V}{\partial S}}{\frac{\partial V}{\partial v}}=\frac{B-rU+rS\frac{\partial U}{\partial S}}{\frac{\partial U}{\partial v}}\tag{A.4}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
the PDE in terms of the price。上式左侧是仅关于V的一个函数，右侧是一个仅关于U的函数，因此两边都可以写成一个关于
\begin_inset Formula $S,v,t$
\end_inset

的函数
\begin_inset Formula $f(S,v,t)$
\end_inset

。根据Heston，将此函数设定为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f(S,v,t)=-\kappa(\bar{v}-v)+\lambda(S,v,t)
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda(S,v,t)$
\end_inset

是波动率风险的价格。因此，将(A.4)左侧替换为
\begin_inset Formula $f(S,v,t)$
\end_inset

可得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial U}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}vS^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial S^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho S\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v\partial S}-rU+rS\frac{\partial U}{\partial S}=[-\kappa(\bar{v}-v)+\lambda(S,v,t)]\frac{\partial U}{\partial v}\tag{A.5}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
teh PDE in terms of the log price。令
\begin_inset Formula $x=lnS$
\end_inset

，用
\begin_inset Formula $x,v,t$
\end_inset

表示的PDE更加简洁。首先需要用到下面一些导数关系式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial U}{\partial S}=\frac{\partial U}{\partial x}\frac{\partial x}{\partial S}=\frac{\partial U}{\partial x}/S
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v\partial S}=\frac{\partial}{\partial x}(\frac{\partial U}{\partial v})\frac{\partial x}{\partial S}=\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v\partial x}/S
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial S^{2}} & =\frac{\partial}{\partial S}(\frac{\partial U}{\partial x}/S)\\
 & =\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial x\partial S}/S+\frac{\partial U}{\partial x}(-\frac{1}{S^{2}})\\
 & =\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial x^{2}}/S^{2}-\frac{\partial U}{\partial x}/S^{2}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

将上式代入(A.5)可得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial U}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}v(\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial x^{2}}-\frac{\partial U}{\partial x})+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v\partial x}-rU+r\frac{\partial U}{\partial x}=[-\kappa(\bar{v}-v)+\lambda(S,v,t)]\frac{\partial U}{\partial v}
\]

\end_inset

或者
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial U}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial x^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v\partial x}-rU+(r-\frac{1}{2}v)\frac{\partial U}{\partial x}+[\kappa(\bar{v}-v)-\lambda(S,v,t)]\frac{\partial U}{\partial v}=0
\]

\end_inset

在Heston model中，假定波动率风险的价格与波动率是线性关系的：
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda(S,v,t)=\lambda v$
\end_inset

，则上式还可以写为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial U}{\partial t}+\frac{1}{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial x^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho\frac{\partial^{2}U}{\partial v\partial x}-rU+(r-\frac{1}{2}v)\frac{\partial U}{\partial x}+[\kappa(\bar{v}-v)-\lambda v]\frac{\partial U}{\partial v}=0\tag{A.6}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection
the Call price
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
call的价值为：
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
C_{T}(K) & =e^{-r\tau}E[(S_{T}-K)^{+}]\\
 & =e^{x_{t}}P_{1}(x,v,\tau)-e^{-r\tau}KP_{2}(x,v,\tau)\tag{A.7}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

与BS公式一样，
\begin_inset Formula $P_{2}(x,v,\tau)$
\end_inset

表示the probability of the call expiring in-the-money
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
the PDE for 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{1}$
\end_inset

and 
\begin_inset Formula $P_{2}$
\end_inset

。根据(A.6)，有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-\frac{\partial C}{\partial\tau}+\frac{1}{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}C}{\partial x^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}C}{\partial v^{2}}+\sigma v\rho\frac{\partial^{2}C}{\partial v\partial x}-rC+(r-\frac{1}{2}v)\frac{\partial C}{\partial x}+[\kappa(\bar{v}-v)-\lambda v]\frac{\partial C}{\partial v}=0\tag{A.8}
\]

\end_inset

由(A.7)知：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial C}{\partial\tau}=e^{x}\frac{\partial P_{1}}{\partial\tau}+re^{-r\tau}KP_{2}-e^{-r\tau}K\frac{\partial P_{2}}{\partial\tau}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial C}{\partial x}=e^{x}P_{1}+e^{x}\frac{\partial P_{1}}{\partial x}-e^{-r\tau}K\frac{\partial P_{2}}{\partial x}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial^{2}C}{\partial x^{2}}=e^{x}P_{1}+2e^{x}\frac{\partial P_{1}}{\partial x}+e^{x}\frac{\partial^{2}P_{1}}{\partial x^{2}}-e^{-r\tau}K\frac{\partial^{2}P_{2}}{\partial x^{2}}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial^{2}C}{\partial v\partial x}=e^{x}\frac{\partial P_{1}}{\partial v}+e^{x}\frac{\partial^{2}P_{1}}{\partial x\partial v}-e^{-r\tau}K\frac{\partial^{2}P_{2}}{\partial x\partial v}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial C}{\partial v}=e^{x}\frac{\partial P_{1}}{\partial v}-e^{-r\tau}K\frac{\partial P_{2}}{\partial v}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial^{2}C}{\partial v^{2}}=e^{x}\frac{\partial^{2}P_{1}}{\partial v^{2}}-e^{-r\tau}K\frac{\partial^{2}P_{2}}{\partial v^{2}}
\]

\end_inset

将它们代入(A.8)，令
\begin_inset Formula $K=0,S=1$
\end_inset

可以得到关于
\begin_inset Formula $P_{1}$
\end_inset

的PDE，令
\begin_inset Formula $K=-1,S=0$
\end_inset

可以得到关于
\begin_inset Formula $P_{2}$
\end_inset

的PDE：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-\frac{\partial P_{j}}{\partial\tau}+\rho\sigma v\frac{\partial^{2}P_{j}}{\partial x\partial v}+\frac{1}{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}P_{j}}{\partial x^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}v\sigma^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}P_{j}}{\partial v^{2}}+(r+u_{j}v)\frac{\partial P_{j}}{\partial x}+(a-b_{j}v)\frac{\partial P_{j}}{\partial v}=0\tag{A.9}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $j=1,2$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $u_{1}=\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $u_{2}=-\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $a=\kappa\bar{v}$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $b_{1}=\kappa+\lambda-\rho\sigma$
\end_inset

，
\begin_inset Formula $b_{2}=\kappa+\lambda$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
Obtaining the characteristic functions。 Heston假定了一个关于
\begin_inset Formula $x=lnS_{T}$
\end_inset

的特征函数，如下：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
f_{j}(\phi;x,v)=exp(C_{j}(\tau,\phi)+D_{j}(\tau,\phi)v_{0}+i\phi x)\tag{A.10}
\]

\end_inset

该特征方程满足(A.9)【this is a consequence of the Feynman-Kac theorem】。于是有：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
-\frac{\partial f_{j}}{\partial\tau}+\rho\sigma v\frac{\partial^{2}f_{j}}{\partial x\partial v}+\frac{1}{2}v\frac{\partial^{2}f_{j}}{\partial x^{2}}+\frac{1}{2}v\sigma^{2}\frac{\partial^{2}f_{j}}{\partial v^{2}}+(r+u_{j}v)\frac{\partial f_{j}}{\partial x}+(a-b_{j}v)\frac{\partial f_{j}}{\partial v}=0\tag{A.11}
\]

\end_inset

通过计算关于
\begin_inset Formula $f_{j}$
\end_inset

的各阶导数，并代入上式，可以得到两个differential equation：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial D_{j}}{\partial\tau}=\rho\sigma i\phi D_{j}-\frac{1}{2}\phi^{2}+\frac{1}{2}\sigma^{2}D_{j}^{2}+u_{j}i\phi-b_{j}D_{j}\tag{A.12}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial C_{j}}{\partial\tau}=ri\phi+aD_{j}
\]

\end_inset

其中，Heston设定了初始条件：
\begin_inset Formula $D_{j}(0,\phi)=0,C_{j}(0,\phi)=0$
\end_inset

。可以看到(A.12)是一个Riccati equation in 
\begin_inset Formula $D_{j}$
\end_inset

，而另一个就是常微分方程(ODE)。
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
solving the Heston Riccati equation。由(A.12)，the Heston Riccati equation可以简写成如下形式：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\partial D_{j}}{\partial\tau}=P_{j}-Q_{j}D_{j}+RD_{j}^{2}\tag{A.13}
\]

\end_inset

相应的二阶ODE是
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\omega''+Q_{j}\omega'+P_{j}R=0\tag{A.14}
\]

\end_inset

因而，(A.13)的解可以写成：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{j}=-\frac{1}{R}(\frac{K\alpha e^{\alpha\tau}+\beta e^{\beta\tau}}{K\alpha e^{\alpha\tau}+e^{\beta\tau}})\tag{A.15}
\]

\end_inset

利用初始条件
\begin_inset Formula $D_{j}(0,\phi)=0$
\end_inset

可以得到：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
D_{j}=\frac{b_{j}-\rho\sigma i\phi+d_{j}}{\sigma^{2}}(\frac{1-e^{d_{j}\tau}}{1-g_{j}e^{d_{j}\tau}})\tag{A.16}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
d_{j}=\sqrt{(\rho\sigma i\phi-b_{j})^{2}-\sigma^{2}(2u_{j}i\phi-\phi^{2})}
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
g_{j}=\frac{b_{j}-\rho\sigma i\phi+d_{j}}{b_{j}-\rho\sigma i\phi-d_{j}}
\]

\end_inset

于是，通过积分可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C_{j}=\int_{0}^{\tau}ri\phi dy+a(\frac{Q_{j}+d_{j}}{2R})\int_{0}^{\tau}(\frac{1-e^{d_{j}y}}{1-g_{j}e^{d_{j}y}})dy+K_{1}\tag{A.17}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $K_{1}$
\end_inset

为常数。再利用初始条件
\begin_inset Formula $C_{j}(0,\phi)=0$
\end_inset

，并且将
\begin_inset Formula $d_{j},Q_{j},g_{j}$
\end_inset

代入可得：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C_{j}=ri\phi\tau+\frac{a}{\sigma^{2}}[(b_{j}-\rho\sigma i\phi+d_{j})\tau-2ln(\frac{1-g_{j}e^{d_{j}\tau}}{1-g_{j}})]\tag{A.18}
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula $a=\kappa\bar{v}$
\end_inset

。
\end_layout

